Why not use a thicker 1/2" plus felt. If you ever have to remove it, it's a
lot easier then the sprayon or dynamat. Plus the cost remains better than
the other two alternatives you have mentioned. Have "felted" my Westfalia
and it is now extremely quiet compared to what it was before

Scott
'67 Westy


